title: 2 Chainz Presents Kevin Durant's "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Playlist
text:
Home > Music > 2 Chainz Presents Kevin Durant's "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Playlist 2 Chainz Presents Kevin Durant's "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" Playlist 0 0 2 Posted by Shaun M , Mar 19, 2017 at 12:27am 2 Chainz teams up with Kevin Durant for the newest edition of "Pretty Girls like Trap Music." 
2 Chainz went off the board this week for his special Pretty Girls Like Trap Music playlists series. The ATL rapper linked up with NBA forward Kevin Durant to present this latest offering. In previous editions, Tity Boi had exclusively worked with women including Nicki Minaj, Cardi B and Erykah Badu . 
Despite the fast approaching playoffs, the star of the Golden State Warriors has been sidelined with a season-ending injury. So he had plenty of time to choose his favorite trap joints. And judging from the list, Durant has got good taste. Durant included Future's "Mask Off," Migos ' "T-Shirt," Travis Scott's "beibs in the trap," and 2 Chainz's "Good Drank 2.0," featuring Quavo, Gucci Mane and the heavenly Trap Choir -- Guwop references KD on it. 
Other acts include Lil Wayne, Drake, Rae Sremmurd, 21 Savage and Metro Boomin , Dave East , A$AP Ferg and more. 
Stream Durant's "Pretty Girls Like Trap Music" playlist on Spotify.
